{"tid":1390710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［吹雞］中大校長段崇智聽日四點龐萬倫見學生","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:50:31.000Z","uid":136083,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ab4f47f65e07fab352a9d46e1e2e4be63a792350","tid":1390710,"uid":136083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"Vice-Chancellor&rsquo;s Meeting with Students<br />\n<br />\nDear Students,<br />\n<br />\nThe Vice-Chancellor and President, Prof Rocky Tuan, will meet with students tomorrow (1 August) to exchange views on recent events in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nDetails are as follow:<br />\n<br />\nDate: \t\t1 August 2019<br />\nTime:\t\t4pm-6pm<br />\nVenue:\t\tG01, Pommerenke Student Centre<br />\nModerator: \tProf. Francis Lee, Director, School of Journalism and Communication<br />\nLanguage: Cantonese/English/Putonghua<br />\n<br />\nAll students of CUHK are welcome by presenting your CU Link card at the registration counter which will open at 3:15pm.  <br />\n<br />\nOffice of Student Affairs<br />\n<br />\n全部中大人同我早啲去霸位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028ecb63d693702c09aacc12e7dc4893bc757e5e","tid":1390710,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"我要罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04755f47907b4ca384a4db14cfef7393f0b3cac9","tid":1390710,"uid":202516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:11:50.000Z","msg":"霸位！！！！！"},{"pid":"9d94250305e205bd8a5f1c99dfad36f559de4b15","tid":1390710,"uid":136083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"暴大學生 assemble"},{"pid":"f3850c57a7cd2a12e1576b1146eabbb5ce07af21","tid":1390710,"uid":136083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite